      <hedline>
        <hl1>Boom Box</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Drew Karydes letter on Michael Lewis's August 13 article note mute button can control television ads (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I have had ''ad zapping'' technology in my house for years. It's one of the great inventions of the last 25 years, yet it gets no press. It's called the mute button.</p>
        <p>Drew Karydes  New York</p>
      </block>
